uid":147586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:35:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要美心流心ok？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同求"},{"pid":"c9196704ceaf02d90c44c31062599d2c2e39e546","tid":427080,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好信啊，豬蛇前排入咗批假月餅想散貨咋！！！</blockquote><br />\n榮華都有假？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n月餅竟是在養雞場生產？會不會加料？廣東惠州執法部門本月20日，查獲一個匿於養雞場的月餅包裝工場。該工場主要仿冒美心、榮華等4個品牌月餅。「廠房」內散裝月餅、包裝盒等隨地堆放，有的甚至被放置在雞糞旁邊。<br />\n<br />\n這個非法月餅工場，匿藏於平山蕉田一個養雞場內。當局指，這個工場並非生產月餅，而是把製成的月餅包裝。工場仿製的主要是4個知名品牌︰香港的榮華、美心、半島月餅，以及深圳的安琪月餅。月餅質素低劣，如流心月餅裏沒有流心，餅皮易碎等。<br />\n<br />\n惠東縣市場監督管理局人員，在現場查封並檢獲該假冒品牌月餅近50,000個、假冒品牌月餅包裝空盒約4,000個，月餅吸塑膠盤共550,000多個，涉案總值超過100萬元人民幣，相關涉事負責人已被公安機關扣查調查。目前，案件正在進一步調查當中。<br />\n<br />\n廣東廣播電視台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170929&amp;guid=57269343&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170929%26guid%3D57269343%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=SWnDTpVlGp35FCDRvsOo89tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2035ad6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170929%26guid%3D57269343%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=02ea59ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170929&amp;guid=57269343&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n中秋前已經回家警告手足，冇回家嘅忤逆仔只能說抵撚死"},{"pid":"32e60396b3778872b0d085bffb178e1cd18c20a9","tid":427080,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"Lamela<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5dff05a025380643adfb8e3ac2c003fcd3d820","tid":427080,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":